INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1021", "1", "2016-08-12 02:50:36", "2016-08-12 02:50:36", "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bootcamp is a mix of cardio and resistance exercise which combine bodyweight exercises with free weight exercises. It will help you to improve your balance, strength and flexibility. A challenging all body free weight workout. Our Bootcamp mixes cardio and resistance exercises to improve your balance, strength and flexibility. Battle Ropes. Slam Balls. Core Bag Lifts. Build your strength. Bootcamp is a challenging free-weight workout for your entire body, increasing strength and improving your definition. Within this class,there is an element of circuits involved. Bootcamp is one of our most popular classes so please book your space. This great overall workout welcomes all fitness levels.\r\nBootcamp classes are up to 1 hour long and are packed full of exercises that keep you moving throughout the room, burning calories and building strength.</p>", "Bootcamp Classes", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "bootcamp-classes", "", "", "2016-08-13 17:09:21", "2016-08-13 17:09:21", "", "0", "http://inwavethemes.com/demo-images/athlete/?post_type=iw_courses&#038;p=1021", "0", "iw_courses", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1023", "1", "2016-08-12 09:17:17", "2016-08-12 09:17:17", "", "Fitness for man", "", "trash", "closed", "closed", "", "fitness-for-man__trashed", "", "", "2016-08-14 06:41:02", "2016-08-14 06:41:02", "", "0", "http://inwavethemes.com/demo-images/athlete/?post_type=iw_courses&#038;p=1023", "0", "iw_courses", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1042", "1", "2016-08-12 02:25:29", "2016-08-12 02:25:29", "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We have a large amount of members that train purely for fitness, weight loss and as a hobby; we then also have a team of amateur boxers and professional boxers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We have years of experience in getting people fit and to a high level of boxing technique, if this sounds interesting to you then please contact us.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We setup the lessons to exactly what you want to get from your training at the gym. If you just want to come down and get fit, learn how to box and take up a new hobby then you do not have to spar or take part in any contact however, you will still be taught like a boxer and trained in the same way minus the contact aspect of the training. If however you are looking to compete in Boxing then we have a FREE sparring session for you.</p>", "Boxing Squad Classes", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "boxing-squad-classes", "", "", "2016-08-14 06:24:27", "2016-08-14 06:24:27", "", "0", "http://inwavethemes.com/demo-images/athlete/?post_type=iw_courses&#038;p=1042", "0", "iw_courses", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1044", "1", "2016-08-12 02:30:21", "2016-08-12 02:30:21", "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Are you looking for a way to keep fit that is not boring but gets you the results you want or preparing for a Bare-Knuckle Competition?\r\nWhether it is getting into shape, losing weight or for a confidence boost at elite Bare-knuckle boxing, we can help you to achieve these goals.\r\nWe offer personalised training programmes with our vast knowledge of Bare-knuckle boxing fitness, circuit training and diet information so you will see results a lot quicker than in a normal gym.\r\nYou will get the full benefits of a boxing class this is not boxercise however it is none contact, you will actually be learning how to box which is great for self-defence, self-confidence and getting fit at the same time!\r\nEvery session is different and enjoyable including skipping, pads, lightweights, and boxing technique.</p>", "Bare-knuckle boxing Classes", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "bare-knuckle-boxing-classes", "", "", "2016-08-14 05:46:01", "2016-08-14 05:46:01", "", "0", "http://inwavethemes.com/demo-images/athlete/?post_type=iw_courses&#038;p=1044", "0", "iw_courses", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1045", "1", "2016-08-12 02:33:02", "2016-08-12 02:33:02", "", "Boxing for Female", "", "trash", "closed", "closed", "", "boxing-for-man__trashed", "", "", "2016-08-14 06:40:25", "2016-08-14 06:40:25", "", "0", "http://inwavethemes.com/demo-images/athlete/?post_type=iw_courses&#038;p=1045", "0", "iw_courses", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1047", "1", "2016-08-12 02:41:04", "2016-08-12 02:41:04", "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Open class sparring is supervised time that is open to anyone who wants to come in and work on their fighting skills and techniques. This class is open to any age or class and is a great way to refine your skills and have fun while doing it.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our open ring is a vital and often-misunderstood part of any Sparring training. The idea is not to try to kill each other! It is an opportunity to put into practice the skills you have been learning in our classes. During an open sparring session, you can decide with your partner what you want to work on; you could work on distance and timing in Boxing, securing and tightening that arm bar or other techniques.</p>", "Open Sparring Classes", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "open-sparring-classes", "", "", "2016-08-13 17:52:17", "2016-08-13 17:52:17", "", "0", "http://inwavethemes.com/demo-images/athlete/?post_type=iw_courses&#038;p=1047", "0", "iw_courses", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1048", "1", "2015-04-02 02:40:38", "2015-04-02 02:40:38", "", "psychology_of_training", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "psychology_of_training", "", "", "2015-04-02 02:40:38", "2015-04-02 02:40:38", "", "0", "http://localhost/gym2/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/psychology_of_training1.jpg", "0", "attachment", "image/jpeg", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1049", "1", "2016-08-12 02:44:08", "2016-08-12 02:44:08", "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">At Underdogz Gym we have had great success in transforming peoples figures and improving their health as well as their fitness, with our training and nutrition plans we make sure that you only lose body fat and not muscle, this is what give you the toned defined look. We have had too many success stories to mention but please check out before and afters for just a couple of the great examples of this.</p>", "Fit Box Classes", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "fit-box-classes", "", "", "2016-08-13 17:43:10", "2016-08-13 17:43:10", "", "0", "http://inwavethemes.com/demo-images/athlete/?post_type=iw_courses&#038;p=1049", "0", "iw_courses", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1050", "1", "2015-04-02 02:43:46", "2015-04-02 02:43:46", "", "streng_training", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "streng_training", "", "", "2015-04-02 02:43:46", "2015-04-02 02:43:46", "", "0", "http://localhost/gym2/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/streng_training1.jpg", "0", "attachment", "image/jpeg", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1051", "1", "2016-08-12 02:45:56", "2016-08-12 02:45:56", "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The aim of Kickboxing Squad Classes is to score punches on your opponent as many times as you can without being hit. We aim to increase your accuracy, hand speed and stamina. Most importantly, your footwork is the key to your success.\r\nThese sessions do not have our normal limit of six people per class there could be up to ten participants in each session however, we always make sure you work hard and enjoy the session.\r\nThere is minimal or no contact involved in the sessions, just practicing of techniques and learning how to use Kick boxing effectively and in an appropriate way. Once we feel you have a good foundation light sparring will be the next step. Every session is different and enjoyable including skipping, pads, lightweights, and boxing technique.</p>", "Kickboxing Squad Classes", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "kickboxing-squad-classes", "", "", "2016-08-13 18:00:28", "2016-08-13 18:00:28", "", "0", "http://inwavethemes.com/demo-images/athlete/?post_type=iw_courses&#038;p=1051", "0", "iw_courses", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("1052", "1", "2016-08-12 02:50:27", "2016-08-12 02:50:27", "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Personal Training at Underdogz Gym is available on booking and is a great way of boosting confidence for starters, or boosting your fitness level if you are a professional. Either way, we customised sessions to suit you.</p>", "Personal Training", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "personal-training", "", "", "2016-08-14 06:38:12", "2016-08-14 06:38:12", "", "0", "http://inwavethemes.com/demo-images/athlete/?post_type=iw_courses&#038;p=1052", "0", "iw_courses", "", "0");
