r format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.", "Contact form 1", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "contact-form-1", "", "", "2016-08-16 12:23:15", "2016-08-16 12:23:15", "", "0", "http://gmswebdesign.net/gym/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=1484", "0", "wpcf7_contact_form", "", "0");
